Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情况开始有了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和个人的想法没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,时机来到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和人们的行动没有联系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  鲁路修一定幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至少  他能靠自己的力量来决定世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.45,0:00:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对任何对手都能下达绝对服从命令的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依赖GEASS的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 21
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(430,430)}学 园 祭 宣 言 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.30,0:02:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为中华联邦的介入和黑色骑士团的恐怖行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,舆论很不安定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是两个不同的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出席数不够是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.85,0:02:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算成绩有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是由菲米娅殿下的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:26.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出席数不够就只能留级
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来还要有点时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天晚上能结束吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的救世主当然是ZERO啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,11区人也能出人头地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看看那枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有ZERO的话九州就被中华联邦夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是新闻没有说这事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚不可能会报道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能和平的话什么都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木朱雀所做的是乞讨来的和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,贫民区的意见也有分歧了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,分成了恭顺派和反抗派
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:03:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  大家都会大吃一惊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果知道ZERO的目的是要建立国家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该更现实一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我赞成ZERO的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着那家伙的话能一下子逆转人生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我成为官僚的梦想也能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,官僚  你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是有梦想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有加入黑色骑士团的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,估计我现在也用上Refrain了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Refrain  你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果用了Refrain就会想起过去和ZERO身份的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只能等待指示无法和ZERO联络
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么按照预定由我来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是陷阱  还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是情报源是需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那边也有希望入团的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且迪哈鲁特制造的逃走途径只有明天能用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:03:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,东京租界最早建立的阿修佛德学园的学园祭开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开始的信号是这个人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真是吵闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎  欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是布里塔尼亚卷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冲击的争议作品  王宫与ZERO  正在上演
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有克洛维斯殿下的照片~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,泽崎也起到利用价值了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来条件大多凑齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各地区的紧急对应方式全都备案了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媒体的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.27,0:04:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,租界里的太阳能光板的分布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,及其能源供给范围已经掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个地下协助人员怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人负责就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经掌握了72%
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正在关注新闻报道  以及对占领目标进行布置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,京都关于假象的计划书也想一起让你确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我会确认
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一件事报告晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,零号队的事  扇副司令…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,危机  大危机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一会再联络你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,危机？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在偷什么懒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修你是执行委员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,进行状况没有问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那部分是会长负责的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去年也只有2米
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子说要做直径12米的批萨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完成的话这个型号就会变成世界第一了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,光是烤炉和食材就费了好大劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且连电视台都请来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吧  我们是不能露脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,批萨的记录是一定要留下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,躲着点就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗  这是会长的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  停
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,利瓦尔  我这边好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  心情很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遇上什么好事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:05:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  有点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  贫民区的11区人一个人来这里不太方便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果害怕布里塔尼亚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用这么介意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  这样真的对你的工作有帮助吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  因为要收集开发计划的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话  应该把她交给警察或医院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的情报如果泄露的话会把别人卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就算这样  灭口这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我是学校的老师  感觉很怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不干了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一个从小就在一起的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他却死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个家伙的梦想换我来实现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这个梦想对我来说负担重了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去里面就有点…  而且我是11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是对外开放的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为两位带路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  这是我们的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你不会再来学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么说来你是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你没有告诉别人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你是卡莲·修坦菲尔德吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是红月卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要卖我人情让我放松警惕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在战场上见面的话我是不会手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是想继续说服你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然明白这是违反规则的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但在学校  比起战斗我更想选择说服这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像变了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀  卡车来了  奶酪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你来学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  身体情况不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:08:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲  刚才的事和在学校没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话卡莲能去教室一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那边人手好像不够
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这种小事的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要爬上来吗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别因为这样就害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  鲁路修那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是鬼屋的话就说清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.11,0:08:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能命令我的只有ZERO啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是情侣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这种地方都需要用机械的话全用机械不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个虽然很轻但太热了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经热得可以和初期的Glasgow媲美了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀  扇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太开心了  学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她只瞄准那个人吗  那人和罗伊德很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然把工作全都甩给她压力太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  批萨是午后开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不是做这种事的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  戏剧部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经和影研的人说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来政变的准备就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手滑了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连军人都  真是和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是朱雀的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  那边那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,世界第一的批萨在哪儿可以吃到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  原来你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真没想到能在一夜之间将18区给…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅军真是优秀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因为有哥哥将自己的正规军借给我的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这点小事是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和在本国待机的格拉斯顿骑士合流
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来就回归到我军本来的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gloucester也有了附加装备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和中华联邦的交涉也能使用到那张牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,光荣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能被笑傲战场的科奈莉娅公主这么拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别调侃我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,战场上的你比舞会上的任何鲜花和蝴蝶还要美丽耀眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  就如同闪光一般
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请别这么说我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲到哪儿去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥都快要出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲的话 她昨晚和我谈过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  还有就是巴托雷在管理的那样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.11,0:10:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但那东西真的有利用价值吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说  世界第一的批萨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会带回来的  你给我留在房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是个大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会在这种事上用策略
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有军人和记者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被找到的话怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚烤好的才好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把变装道具拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我正因为学园祭和政变的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么到学校里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不是11区人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是除相关人员外禁止入内的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扇？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有无论如何都要和朱雀说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲  我认为这个想法很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要按你所相信的道路走下去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会去和科奈莉娅谈一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀  哥哥承认我的想法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我才该道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:11:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道  这个声音是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扇既然被看到了就只能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果C.C.在这里被看到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,液化气的钢瓶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得备用的好像在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你那里有备用的钢瓶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,利瓦尔在找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想应该在相反的方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用GEASS就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对扇和不知道身份的人使用太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的人全都使用过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这叫自作自受  谁让你滥用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊  现在这情况还…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话我有话要对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你先一个人逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一会儿再说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会引起一场骚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  现在说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这种时候根本碰不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  木板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  别呆在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这个烟雾是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,漏气的喷枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像被木板压坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先不管这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁能来帮我一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,脚上有一种熟悉的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让你卷进奇怪的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很久没有这种紧张心跳的感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,离开11区吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话袭击你的人也就找不到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的我会比现在更幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能继续你刚才的话题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人是我的…什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我即使成为11区人也愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能保密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于哥哥和我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要能和哥哥在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得那时候两个人吵架的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们谁能成为哥哥的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还说『今天晚上就决定谁能成』让鲁路修头痛了好一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你还是对哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  马上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,世界第一的批萨的制作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,另提一下  我脚下的是只为这次使用的特制烤炉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美好的预算浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白  莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会好好准备一个时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以B班现在去帮助舞台工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  真是轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以为自己不知道就代表所有人都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害啊  看来能按时完成工作了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近对差遣人的工作比较熟练了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大家还真是轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近才刚刚发生了中华联邦进攻过来的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,节日是需要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管对谁而言  不管什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还太嫩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我上了一课啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉  批萨还…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事联络我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,食材的准备也完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么由我来介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,制作的机器是阿修佛德的Ganymede
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[Ganymede:第三代KnightMare Frame的代表性机体]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经是很传统的机体了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  操纵的人既是我们学生会的风纪委员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是由菲米娅的骑士  枢木朱雀~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  11区人也来了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是开放的学园庆典  而且是朱雀所在的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀对11区人来说是希望之星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第三世代KnightMare  Ganymede
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是『闪光的玛丽安娜』所使用的机体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个只有基本骨架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是庆典用的人偶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为玛丽安娜王妃的去世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而从次时代的竞争中脱离的异端机体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然结婚的目的是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人对异性没有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是有概念的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太漂亮了  竟能做得那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀同学  大家都在期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去年这还是我的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但比不上本职的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天遇到太多让人吃惊的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修和娜娜莉竟然就在这么近的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是朱雀的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么啊  那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是和女人混在一起的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不希望大家得不到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  今天是最后一次见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我找到了一个好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,勒鲁…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说是由菲米娅殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.36,0:17:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊  是由菲米娅殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅殿下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修  把娜娜莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  就这么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  副总督好像在正面通路附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  会让待机部队行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,摄像机准备  让转播室准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅殿下好像来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪儿  在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,危险  请不要奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会摔倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,批萨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道应该交给专业人员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是要放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在很多事上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是身为副总督的第三皇女殿下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢您的协力  接下来交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,HI电视台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.82,0:18:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请说句话  只说一句也行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅殿下  我是妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请到这里避难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  靠自力能够逃走的话是最好了  副司令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:18:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我这边还没有完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好的器材空间没有用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,零号队队长也没有逃走的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想让你就这样作为密探在租界内活动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我总有一天会介绍你给ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有事吧  由菲米娅殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吧  娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  由菲姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:31.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她没事  朱雀救了她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲姐姐说她和朱雀交往的不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很相配吧  那个两人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉  你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅殿下  请接受采访
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个影像能向11区全面播放吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直播吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有重要的事要发表
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下  由菲米娅殿下她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她又干了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在切换紧急播放内容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是神圣布里塔尼亚帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.39,0:20:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,11区副总督  由菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我有事想要告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  小姑娘这么小题大做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  由菲米娅·Li·布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宣言在富士山周边建立行政特区  日本
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  布里塔尼亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,承认 日本
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有这一手吗  虽然有地域限制
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这行政特区日本  11区人能拿回日本人这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对11区人的限制和布里塔尼亚人的特权
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个特区日本不会存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚人也好  11区人也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是平等的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个情况我考虑过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那只是梦想而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到了吗  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会揭开你的过去和假面下的面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.18,0:21:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以请你也加入这个日本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO  怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛维斯殿下怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.10,0:21:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO  和我一起在布里塔尼亚里创造新的未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说是日本人  到现在才…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为情人是11区人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被摆了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来  不管选择哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团都会被毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会没有存在的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会被这种情况轻易地…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样  你想把所有都得到手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.55,0:21:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连我们生活的地方也一并都…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.55,0:21:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:22:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么都没有看到  没有听到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是隐藏面貌的恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.98,0:22:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修  又能像以前一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经和以前不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.04,0:22:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.94,0:23:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行政特区日本
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,协力的话武力会被取走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反对的话会与民众为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.55,0:24:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团就此失败
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个天真地将善意作为自己装饰的第三皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.58,0:24:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我和娜娜莉来说
